name: WIZ.AI
description: Wiz AI is a cutting-edge Conversational Voice AI technology that is revolutionizing B2C communication. It offers a hyper-personalized, omnichannel customer engagement solution that enables businesses of all sizes to seamlessly engage with customers through Voice call and WhatsApp business API. As a leading industry player, Wiz AI's Talkbot has significantly enhanced ROI across a wide range of sectors, including Banking, Insurance, Fintech, Telecommunications, E-commerce, Healthcare, and Government. With an extensive range of capabilities, features, and benefits, the Talkbot, along with the WhatsApp Business API solution, is poised to transform the customer experience landscape.
